{"id":334376,"date":[{"year":1956,"month":10,"day":6}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"小花杂拾","genre":"","count":"98","ytitle":"","mtitle":"小花杂拾","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"◇如果有人问我:诗人是什么?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我将简捷地回答:多情的战士。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"◇要有这样的胸襟和气魄，说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"获得能使我满足，给予更能使我满足。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"◇思想劳动是艰苦的，但也是快乐的。越思索，越向真理接近。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(维)"}]}